	2.	uDeploy (UrbanCode Deploy): Manages application deployment automation across multiple environments.
	3.	Bitbucket: Hosts Git repositories, enabling pull requests and collaboration.
	4.	CloudBees CD: Orchestrates end-to-end software delivery pipeline with automation.
	5.	CloudBees CI: Enhances Jenkins with enterprise-level continuous integration capabilities.
	6.	Sonar: Ensures code quality by detecting bugs, vulnerabilities, and duplications.
	7.	Jenkins: Supports continuous integration and continuous delivery in DevOps pipelines.
